<i>noun</i>: 화기 [화ː기], 소요 [소요], 동요 [동ː요] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>화기 [화ː기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heat of fire</dd><br>
<dd>불에서 나오는 뜨거운 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>The hot air created from fire.</dd><br>
<dd>2. frustration; agitation</dd><br>
<dd>가슴이 어수선하고 답답해지는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of restlessness and frustration.</dd><br>
<dd>3. burst of anger; sudden anger</dd><br>
<dd>걸핏하면 화를 벌컥 내는 증세.</dd><br>
<dd>A symptom of flying into a rage easily.</dd><br>
<dd>4. burning sensation</dd><br>
<dd>불에 덴 자리에서 올라오는 화끈거리는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>A burning sensation coming from the area affected by a burn.</dd><br>
<dt>소요 [소요]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; commotion; agitation; riot</dd><br>
<dd>여러 사람이 시끄럽게 들고일어남. 또는 그런 소란.</dd><br>
<dd>A loud protest caused by a group of people, or such a disturbance.</dd><br>
<dt>동요 [동ː요]</dt><br>
<dd>1. tremble; shake</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 이리저리 흔들림.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which an object is shaken all about.</dd><br>
<dd>2. restlessness</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 마음이 정해지지 않고 자꾸 달라짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An opinion or mind continuing to change without being fixed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. agitation; disturbance</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 제도나 상황이 안정되지 않아 혼란스러움.</dd><br>
<dd>A confusion from an instability in a system or situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>